{
  "stem": "210.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was like from the-- from the-- it was like if they had to go into their house, that it was open like this, and this was the room that they gave me.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In order for me to have privacy, he sent some people and made a door.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I lived there till we got-- we got sent out from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But while there, I-- you know, in the ghetto, there was-- there was, like, a gentleman's agreement.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If I worked in this factory, let's say, and they always got orders to take out, let's say, 2,000 people, 500 people, 5,000 people, they, they always would.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And and they just came, and they took away the children, the sick people, the thing-- you know, and always eliminated people from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then it-- they took already whoever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they made up, let's say, if somebody worked the, in another factory, so they put you on a list.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, they always had to make these lists to send people out because constantly, they were sending people out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And since I was by myself in the ghetto-- so the people that were by themselves, they were first to go because they figured you're not breaking up a family, or you're not making unhappy a family.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he would come to me and would say, Shava, I have to put you on the list, but you're not going to go.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I have to put you because all these people-- because they had to put out a list on the-- on the wall that tomorrow those, and those, and those people had to go into this and this place to go-- to be deported.",
      "word_count": 44
    }
  ],
